      "seed": 1686980146,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 1193055979,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772961572684,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4) Un guardia desordenado\n(1518-11-02 00:10) wakes up\n(1518-11-02 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-01 23:58) Guard #10 begins shift\n\nTras ordenar:\n(1518-11-01 23:58) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-02 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-02 00:10) wakes up\n\nnaps: {10: [(5, 9)]}\n  Siesta 1: min 5, 6, 7, 8, 9\n  Todos freq 1 → most_common devuelve 5\n\nguard = 10, minute = 5\n10 * 5 = 50",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4) Un guardia desordenado\n(1518-11-02 00:10) wakes up\n(1518-11-02 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-01 23:58) Guard #10 begins shift\n\nTras ordenar:\n(1518-11-01 23:58) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-02 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-02 00:10) wakes up\n\nnaps: {10: [(5, 9)]}\n  Siesta 1: min 5, 6, 7, 8, 9\n  Todos freq 1 → most_common devuelve 5\n\nguard = 10, minute = 5\n10 * 5 = 50",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_2Jm1OYJ1C6FaboR_wqCI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1538.8466755535899,
      "y": 10089.81334436429,
      "width": 582.7354125976562,
      "height": 440,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c0Jq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 712843250,
      "version": 163,
      "versionNonce": 936173893,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772961572684,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5) Varios guardias gana la frecuencia más alta\n(1518-11-01 00:00) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-01 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-01 00:10) wakes up\n(1518-11-02 00:00) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-02 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-02 00:10) wakes up\n(1518-11-03 00:00) Guard #20 begins shift\n(1518-11-03 00:15) falls asleep\n(1518-11-03 00:20) wakes up\n(1518-11-04 00:00) Guard #30 begins shift\n(1518-11-04 00:25) falls asleep\n(1518-11-04 00:30) wakes up\n\nnaps: {10: [(5, 9), (5, 9)], 20: [(15, 19)], 30: [(25, 29)]}\n  Guard 10: min 5-9 con freq 2\n  Guard 20: min 15-19 con freq 1\n  Guard 30: min 25-29 con freq 1\n  Guard 10 gana porque tiene la mayor frecuencia en un solo minuto (2 > 1)\n\nguard = 10, minute = 5\n10 * 5 = 50",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5) Varios guardias gana la frecuencia más alta\n(1518-11-01 00:00) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-01 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-01 00:10) wakes up\n(1518-11-02 00:00) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-02 00:05) falls asleep\n(1518-11-02 00:10) wakes up\n(1518-11-03 00:00) Guard #20 begins shift\n(1518-11-03 00:15) falls asleep\n(1518-11-03 00:20) wakes up\n(1518-11-04 00:00) Guard #30 begins shift\n(1518-11-04 00:25) falls asleep\n(1518-11-04 00:30) wakes up\n\nnaps: {10: [(5, 9), (5, 9)], 20: [(15, 19)], 30: [(25, 29)]}\n  Guard 10: min 5-9 con freq 2\n  Guard 20: min 15-19 con freq 1\n  Guard 30: min 25-29 con freq 1\n  Guard 10 gana porque tiene la mayor frecuencia en un solo minuto (2 > 1)\n\nguard = 10, minute = 5\n10 * 5 = 50",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
